description: [``botocore``] This feature allows customers to retrieve runtime statistics for completed queries
[``botocore``] Update cloudwatch client to latest version
[``botocore``] Documentation updates for Database Migration Service (DMS).
[``botocore``] This release includes a new exception type "EC2InstanceUnavailableException" for SendSSHPublicKey and SendSerialConsoleSSHPublicKey APIs.

[``botocore``] The release introduces Account Takeover Insights (ATI) model. The ATI model detects fraud relating to account takeover. This release also adds support for new variable types: ARE_CREDENTIALS_VALID and SESSION_ID and adds new structures to Model Version APIs.
[``botocore``] Added asynchronous API to ingest bulk historical and current data into IoT SiteWise.
[``botocore``] Amazon Kendra now provides Oauth2 support for SharePoint Online. For more information, see https://docs.aws.amazon.com/kendra/latest/dg/data-source-sharepoint.html
[``botocore``] Network Firewall now supports referencing dynamic IP sets from stateful rule groups, for IP sets stored in Amazon VPC prefix lists.
[``botocore``] Adds support for creating an RDS Proxy for an RDS for MariaDB database.
